div.div:
Details
Step #1
ERP updates frequently the Static Inventory
Step #2
ERP updates frequently the Dynamic Inventory
Step #3
Microservices has permissions to access both Inventory list: Static and Dynamic
Microservice has twoSynchronous Real Time Connections
3.a is responsible to access the Static Inventory
3.b is responsible to access the Dynamic Inventory
Step #4
Microservice updates the Temp Table only if these connections can access the Dynamic and Static Inventory
Temp table contains only the Delta
Step #5
Microservice adds an error if he can't access the Static or Dynamic Inventory
Step #6
Cronjob frequently update SFCC.
